	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes.&nbsp;&nbsp;Sai's can be used for piercing.  But they were also used as 1hb weapons historically as well.  The first Sai was generally used to tangle the weapon up and hold it firm and the second Sai was used as a hammer (Read: 1hb) and slammed through the blade of the oponent rendering them weaponless (Or at least with one less sword)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
